verbs.description: [ARG0: six local judges] [V: vie] [ARG2: for florida supreme court vacancies] six judges who handle cases in the tampa bay area are being considered to fill three upcoming vacancies on the florida supreme court the vacancies are a result of the impending departures of jus judge samuel salario jr attorney assistant general counsel second district court of appeal carlos genaro muniz supreme court mark klingensmith john stargel scott pat siracusa tatiana radi salvador rick scott robert long jr court tampa bay bryan scott gowdy hillsborough circuit eric roberson league of women voters bill nelson contesting laurel lee jeffrey kuntz florida supreme court gov rick scott prosecutor r fred lewis anthony michael tatti u s county judge mark mahon carlton fields cynthia cox howard coates thomas ramsberger barbara pariente patrick o'byrne haden andrew atkinson judge samuel salario jr florida sen tom lee mark miller ross bilbrey supreme court of florida peggy quince sen bill nelson michael andrews
